import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Link, Grid } from '@mui/material';

export const Footer = () => (
  <Box component="footer" bgcolor="#0d3b66" color="white" border={10} py={5} px={3} mt={10}>
    <Grid container spacing={4} maxWidth="lg" mx="auto"
      sx={{
        border: '1px solid #991111',
        display: 'flex',
        justifyContent: 'space-between'
      }}
    >
      <Grid item xs={12} md={3} sx={{lineHeight: '2.1'}}>
        <Typography variant="h6" mb={2}>Institucional</Typography>
        <Link href="/diretoria" color="inherit" underline="hover" display="block">Diretoria</Link>
        <Link href="/espaco-aereo" color="inherit" underline="hover" display="block">Espaço aéreo</Link>
        <Link href="/estatuto" color="inherit" underline="hover" display="block">Estatuto</Link>
        <Link href="/regimento-interno" color="inherit" underline="hover" display="block">Regimento Interno</Link>
        <Link href="#" color="inherit" underline="hover" display="block">Sobre</Link>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={12} md={3} sx={{lineHeight: '2.1'}}>
        <Typography variant="h6" mb={2}>Rampa</Typography>
        <Link href="https://www.google.com/maps/@-21.7716455,-46.5746857,17z?entry=ttu">
        <Typography>Mapa</Typography></Link>
        <Typography>WP: -21.7715658,-46.5749861</Typography>
        <Typography>Altitude: 1550m</Typography>
        <Typography>Desnível: 400m</Typography>
        <Typography>Quadrante: S | NE | N | NW</Typography>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={12} md={3} sx={{lineHeight: '2.1'}}>
        <Typography variant="h6" mb={2}>Mídias Sociais</Typography>
        <Link href="https://facebook.com/cpvlpocos/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" color="inherit" underline="hover" display="block">Facebook</Link>
        <Link href="https://instagram.com/cpvloficial" target="_blank" rel="noopener" color="inherit" underline="hover" display="block">Instagram</Link>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
    <Typography textAlign="center" mt={4}>© Clube Poçoscaldense de Vôo Livre - CPVL</Typography>
  </Box>



);
